{"type":"message","id":"bc688b2a","parentId":"33c43650","timestamp":"2026-03-31T02:11:49.586Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！有cron相关的文件。让我看看 cron-cli 或者相关的配置。实际上，我应该看看 .openclaw/config 或者类似的配置目录。\n\n不过更直接的方法是：既然已经有一个脚本可以运行，让我直接查看之前的cron job使用的脚本。从消息来看，任务叫\"股票分析推送_10AM\"，让我搜索一下这个名称。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_96b35fed58bf466eaf324c27","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw; Get-ChildItem -Recurse -Include \"*.json\",\"*.md\",\"*.txt\" | Select-String -Pattern \"股票分析推送\" -List | Select-Object -First 5 Path"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":656,"output":199,"cacheRead":22614,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23469,"cost":{"input":0.00039359999999999997,"output":0.0004378,"cacheRead":0.0024875400000000003,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0033189400000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774923100541}}
